data.description: This 3 bed, 2 bath house is located on a large corner lot in the established neighborhood of Oakdale Mini Farms in Crestview.  Its more than 2000 square feet include an expansive open living space with dining just off of the kitchen which has its own separate eating area. The bedrooms are large enough to fit a king size bed.  The back yard has shed and a gazebo for relaxing or entertaining. The metal roof was installed in 2017, HVAC is 2017 and the water heater is 2019. This house has also had every window replaced so all the hard stuff is done! Please consider this house for your next home.
